{"an8.31:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 8.31 ","an8.31:0.2":"4. Danavagga ","an8.31:0.3":"Pathamadanasutta ","an8.31:1.1":"“Atthimani, bhikkhave, danani. ","an8.31:1.2":"Katamani attha? ","an8.31:1.3":"Asajja danam deti, ","an8.31:1.4":"bhaya danam deti, ","an8.31:1.5":"‘adasi me’ti danam deti, ","an8.31:1.6":"‘dassati me’ti danam deti, ","an8.31:1.7":"‘sahu danan’ti danam deti, ","an8.31:1.8":"‘aham pacami, ime na pacanti; narahami pacanto apacantanam danam adatun’ti danam deti, ","an8.31:1.9":"‘imam me danam dadato kalyano kittisaddo abbhuggacchati’ti danam deti, ","an8.31:1.10":"cittalankaracittaparikkharattham danam deti. ","an8.31:1.11":"Imani kho, bhikkhave, attha danani”ti. ","an8.31:1.12":"Pathamam. "}